articles.title: DPRK FM Meets New Turkish Ambassador
articles.content:
DPRK FM Meets New Turkish Ambassador

					Pyongyang, November 23 (KCNA) -- Foreign Minister of the DPRK Pak Ui Chun Wednesday met and had a talk with new Turkish Ambassador to the DPRK Mustafa Naci Saribas who paid a courtesy call on him.

articles.title: Credentials of Turkish Ambassador to DPRK Accepted
articles.content:
Credentials of Turkish Ambassador to DPRK Accepted

					Pyongyang, November 23 (KCNA) -- Kim Yong Nam, president of the Presidium of the DPRK Supreme People's Assembly, received credentials from Turkish Ambassador to the DPRK Mustafa Naci Saribas at the Mansudae Assembly Hall Wednesday.
					
					After receiving the credentials, Kim had a talk with the ambassador.

articles.title: Chinese Delegation Departs for Home
articles.content:
Chinese Delegation Departs for Home

					Pyongyang, November 23 (KCNA) -- A Chinese delegation of Jilin Yuwen High School headed by Secretary of the School Party Committee Wang Chunguang went back home on Wednesday.
